# WattIf backend configuration. Copy to .env and fill in as needed.
#
# The reasoning-agent layer is PROVIDER-AGNOSTIC. It uses whichever provider is
# configured (Anthropic preferred when both are set); if neither is set it falls back
# to deterministic rule-based rationales — nothing breaks and the sim always runs.

# --- (a) Anthropic (claude-opus-4-7 / claude-sonnet-4-6) -----------------
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# WATTIF_CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-7

# --- (b) OpenAI-compatible gateway ("feather" multi-model key) -----------
# One key, many models, OpenAI-compatible. Used via the openai SDK with base_url.
# Set ALL of API_KEY + BASE_URL (and a MODEL) to enable this provider.
FEATHER_API_KEY=
FEATHER_BASE_URL=
# FEATHER_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# --- scripted demo provider ----------------------------------------------
# When NO real key is set, a deterministic scripted "demo" provider drives the agentic
# planner (full tool-calling loop, auto+step) and keeps rich rule-based voices — so the
# whole experience works with no key. A real key above always takes precedence.
# Set to 0 to fall back to the bare deterministic planner-lite instead.
# WATTIF_DEMO_LLM=1

# --- optional sim/data overrides (sane defaults baked in) ----------------
# WATTIF_LLM_AGENT_SAMPLE=8
# WATTIF_NUM_AGENTS=3000
# WATTIF_SEED=42
# WATTIF_START_YEAR=2025
# WATTIF_TICK_SECONDS=1.0
# WATTIF_CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://127.0.0.1:5173
